snippet.title: Backyard Rain Soundscape demo
snippet.description:
Demo of a Playdate "game" which plays nature soundscape audio as seamless loop for background listening. 

Audio from Playdate sounds *so* good, we need some natural soundscapes on it. This app plays rain ambience recorded in my backyard in an infinite loop. 

If you have a Playdate, download here: 
https://briandorsey.itch.io/backyard-rain-soundscape
